.TH "device_driver_attach" 9 "device_driver_attach" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
device_driver_attach \- attach a specific driver to a specific device
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" device_driver_attach
.BI "(struct device_driver *drv "  ","
.BI "struct device *dev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "drv" 12
Driver to attach
.IP "dev" 12
Device to attach it to
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Manually attach driver to a device. Will acquire both \fIdev\fP lock and
\fIdev->parent\fP lock if needed.
